This backend connects to two AI services:

Backend API â†’  https://backend-geneses-ai.onrender.com

All backend routes are prefixed with /coding_project or /prompts.

ðŸš€ Coding Project APIs (/coding_project/...)
1. Health Check

GET /coding_project/health
âœ… Test connection with AI service.

2. Select Language

POST /coding_project/select-language
Body (JSON):

{
  "language": "Python"
}

3. Get Lesson

GET /coding_project/get-lesson/{lesson_number}?session_id=YOUR_SESSION_ID
Example:

/coding_project/get-lesson/1?session_id=abc123

4. Ask Tutor

POST /coding_project/ask-tutor
Body (JSON):

{
  "session_id": "abc123",
  "question": "Explain Python loops"
}

5. Generate Quiz

GET /coding_project/generate-quiz/{lesson_number}
Example:

/coding_project/generate-quiz/2

6. Submit Quiz

POST /coding_project/submit-quiz
Body (JSON):

{
  "lesson_id": "lesson_2",
  "answers": ["A", "B", "C"]
}

7. Session Status

GET /coding_project/session-status

8. Available Languages

GET /coding_project/available-languages

9. Generate Coding Challenge

GET /coding_project/generate-coding-challenge

10. Submit Code

POST /coding_project/submit-code
Body (JSON):

{
  "challenge_id": "ch123",
  "code": "print('Hello World')"
}

